description: Try our easy to follow Zucchini, Pea & Cheese Frittata recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Frittata,Zucchini,Low saturated fat,High fibre,High protein,Low salt,Christmas,Egg,Low sugar
name: Zucchini, Pea & Cheese Frittata Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat 1 tbs oil in a frying pan over medium heat. Add zucchini and half the onion and cook, turning, until golden.
Preheat grill on high. Whisk eggs in a large bowl. Stir in cheese, peas and half of the salad mix. Season. Pour egg mixture into pan over zucchini and cook for 1215 minutes or until egg is just set.
Transfer pan to grill and cook for 5 minutes or until top is golden and mixture is cooked through.
Cut frittata into wedges and serve topped with remaining salad and onion.
